{"article_id":"Bdj9YlmscKSjMIPq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In recent weeks , some legal scholars have suggested","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Speaker Nancy Pelosi could consider refusing to transmit the articles of impeachment","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that passed the House on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"where Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has declared","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"he is coordinating trial strategy with the White House .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Though the request initially seemed to have little currency on Capitol Hill ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"it gained momentum in recent days","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as McConnell has continued to make clear","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"he has little interest","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"in serving as an impartial overseer of the Senate trial .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Hoyer said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Democratic colleagues have approached him in recent days ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"citing an op-ed by constitutional lawyer Laurence Tribe","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"in which he calls on Democrats to delay sending impeachment articles to the Senate","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"until McConnell agrees to run a fairer process .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"\" Under the current circumstances , such a proceeding would fail to render a meaningful verdict of acquittal , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Tribe wrote .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Notably , House Judiciary Committee Democrats huddled with Tribe earlier this month","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"as they practiced behind closed doors for their series of impeachment hearings .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Pelosi ' s remarks ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"which were barely audible above the clatter of camera shutters ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"were so unexpected","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that they prompted reporters to shout over each other ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"interrupting the speaker at times","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and generating confusion about the next steps in the impeachment process .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" So you may not send them ? \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"one reporter interjected ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to which Pelosi responded :","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"\" You ' re asking me ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"' So are we all going to go out and play in the snow ? '","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"That has not been part of our conversations . \"","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"The last-minute twist was a stunning coda to the monthslong House impeachment process","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that had been meticulously choreographed by Pelosi and other senior Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"After the news conference , Pelosi huddled with top committee chairs","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"leading Trump-focused investigations ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and they emerged with a consistent message :","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"The only story","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that matters","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"is the president has been impeached .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"\" The only thing","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that matters","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"is the president of the United States was impeached today , \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"said Financial Services Chairwoman Maxine Waters","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"( D-Calif. ) .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"As for the Senate ?","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" One step at a time , \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" We defended the Constitution","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and we defended our democracy , \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"said Judiciary Chairman Jerry Nadler","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"( D-N.Y. ) .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"\" Right now , that ' s the story , \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Some Democrats said","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"they became convinced","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"a delay","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"in transmitting articles","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"was under consideration","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"when House leaders decided against naming impeachment managers","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"- the set of lawmakers","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who would argue their case on the Senate floor -","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"until an undetermined later date .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"When President Bill Clinton was impeached in 1998 ,","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"House leaders identified their impeachment managers the same day .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"But Pelosi instead will be empowered to pick managers at her discretion and without a deadline .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"\" The rule will allow the speaker to name managers at any point","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"after the articles pass , \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"a senior House Democratic aide said ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that the House needs to name managers","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"in order to transmit the articles to the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Rep. Earl Blumenauer","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"( D-Ore. )","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"he 's approached every member of House leadership about the idea","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"and received responses","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"ranging from interest to outright support .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Pelosi , in particular , \" indicated","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"she was interested","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and considering it . \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"\" As long as we have the articles of impeachment under our control ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"we have an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"to prevent a travesty , \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Blumenauer said .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Blumenauer argued","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"that the House could use the delay","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"to continue to build on its evidence for impeachment ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and possibly to score additional legal victories","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that could unlock troves of new evidence and witness testimony","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that the Trump administration has withheld from Congress .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Some of those court cases could be decided within weeks .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"\" You can continue to build the record ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"you can get information","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"and you argue for fairness","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"and do n't surrender","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"until it ' s clear that that is in the best interest of the process , \"","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Blumenauer said .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"In his remarks to reporters , Hoyer emphasized","depth":3},{"id":100,"text":"that early discussions about the timing","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"of transmitting articles of impeachment to the Senate are \" not in the context \" of Tribe ' s proposal .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"But he said","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"colleagues keep raising it .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"\" People have read that article ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"discussed it .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"People have come up to me ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"discussed it , \"","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"he said ,","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"adding ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"\" We will talk about it in some point in time .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"It ' s within the speaker ' s purview , obviously ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"she ' ll make that decision .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"And I also think","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"she ' ll do it in discussions with McConnell and [ Senate Minority Leader Chuck ] Schumer . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"pa